title: Detroit Roast Session W DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller And Chico Bean | Ep. 191
itunes:title: Detroit Roast Session W DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller And Chico Bean | Ep. 191
description:
Detroit turnt all the way up and brought the tittays to the building! DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean shut Detroit down with another classic comedy show recorded in front of a live audience at the legendary Fillmore Theater! The fellas do what they do best, roast everybody in the audience - especially the afro brothers - and create brand new jams live with the 85 South Show band! It's Detroit so you know the crew had to pay respect to the city and it's musical legacy. It's the coldest comedy podcast and a stand up comedy show all in one - It's The 85 South Show!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
